latestIgtvVideos.title: Bitsy Rolls
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Ingredients:

Capsicum/Shimla Mirch
Onion 🧅/Piyaaj
Butter 50gms
Tomato ketchup
Pizza Sauce
Salt As Per Tasty 😋
Pizza Seasoning
Chill Felix
Momo Chutney/Salsa Sauce/other Sauce (not mandatory) 

For Rolls Stuffing
1 Capsicum/Shimla Mirch
1 Onion 🧅/Piyaaj
Momo Chutney/Salsa Sauce/other Sauce (not mandatory) 
Pizza Seasoning
Chill Felix
Salt as per Tasty 

For Dough
250 gms Maida/Refine Flour
Oil / Melted Butter 🧈
Salt
Pinch of Baking soda

Step 1:
Take all Roll Stuff into a bowl . Mix all ingredients together. 
Leave for 10 min for rest . 

Step 2:
Take 250gms of Maida add 2-3 tbsp oil, salt as per tasty, pinch of baking soda then make a dough. 
Leave for 10-15 min to marinate

Step 3:
After 10-15 min take a dough to make paratha. 
After that take a fork make some small holes on paratha (it helps to bake Easily.) 

Step 4: 
After making paratha. Spread butter,pizza sauce and stuffing on top of the paratha. Roll Paratha's and cut into a small pieces

Step 5:
Take a Container, grease it with Butter/oil and dust some maida on it. Place all the bitsy Roll. 

Step  6 :
Pre Heat Kadhai for 10 mins
Place Container in kadhai
Bake for 20-30 min at medium flame . 
*If you have microwave then pre heart microwave for 5 min after that put container on it for 15-20 min at 180°C

Yeahh! Your Stuff Bitsy Roll Is Ready
Try This! 
Share your experience with us 🧡
If you like my recipe please share with your friends and love onces ❤
